data.description: Welcome to 2041 N 69th.  This charming, ranch-style 3 bedroom, 1 bath home features a cozy living room with a conjoining dining room.  The property has a large primary bedroom and two additional spacious bedrooms all with great closet space and one big bathroom that also contains main floor washer and dryer hook ups, an open kitchen and mudroom off the back of the house.  Enjoy hanging out in the climate controlled detached two-stall garage or from the privacy of your fenced in yard.  Conveniently located in Bethany Heights, this is a perfect starter home!  Schedule your private showing today.
